      <title>尽管英国前景和汽车金融规定，劳埃德利润仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lloyds-profit-jumps-sets-aside-450-million-pounds-motor-finance-review-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，劳埃德银行集团 (Lloyds Banking Group) 公布 2023 年利润增长 57%，原因是英国经济步履蹒跚，汽车金融监管审查带来的潜在成本未能对其业绩造成重大影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/lloyds-profit-jumps-sets-aside-450-million-pounds-motor-finance-review-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:17:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
